      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>Agents are a blend of the Charmer and Maquis classes, with their need for covert action and deception.</p>\n<p>They may be M.I.6 operatives, or perhaps double agents working for the Abwehr.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\">Advancement</h2>\n<table style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:503px;margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-size:14px;border-right-style:solid;border-left-style:solid;height:107px\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">\n<tr style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;height:27px\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;padding-left:0px;width:114px;height:27px;text-align:center\"><strong>Level</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>XP</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>HD</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>BHB</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>ST</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;height:16px\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:96px;height:16px;text-align:center\">1</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:84px;height:16px;text-align:center\">0</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:87px;height:16px;text-align:center\">1</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:114px;height:16px;text-align:center\">0</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:114px;height:16px;text-align:center\">15</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;height:16px\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:96px;height:16px;text-align:center\">2</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:84px;height:16px;text-align:center\">1250</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:87px;height:16px;text-align:center\">2</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:114px;height:16px;text-align:center\">0</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:114px;height:16px;text-align:center\">14</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;height:16px\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:96px;height:16px;text-align:center\">3</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:84px;height:16px;text-align:center\">2500</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:87px;height:16px;text-align:center\">3+1</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:114px;height:16px;text-align:center\">1</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:114px;height:16px;text-align:center\">13</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;height:16px\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:96px;height:16px;text-align:center\">4</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:84px;height:16px;text-align:center\">5000</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:87px;height:16px;text-align:center\">4</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:114px;height:16px;text-align:center\">1</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:114px;height:16px;text-align:center\">12</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;height:16px\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:96px;height:16px;text-align:center\">5</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:84px;height:16px;text-align:center\">10000</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:87px;height:16px;text-align:center\">5</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:114px;height:16px;text-align:center\">2</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:114px;height:16px;text-align:center\">11</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<h2>Abilities</h2>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Conceal Items</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Conceal Self</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Detect Deception</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Smooth Operator</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\">Saving Throws</h2>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Agents receive a <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">+2 </strong>bonus to all Saving Throws made to resist attempts to influence them or detect when they are being deceptive.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\"><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\" />XP Bonus</h2>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Agents with an Intelligence of 13 or 14 receive a 5% Experience Bonus, and those with 15 or higher get 10%.</li>\n</ul>"
      },
